    title: Oil production – Etemad and Luciana
    description: This dataset covers historical oil production data compiled from two sources. Data from 1900–1980 is sourced from Bouda Etemad and Jean Luciani, "World Energy Production 1800–1985" (ISBN 2-600-56007-6). Data from 1980 onward is sourced from the US Energy Information Administration (EIA), International Energy Statistics.
